file.name: multiple-operations.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Simple API overview
  version: 2.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /someService:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: "-"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Component'
      operationId: getService
    post:
      operationId: postService
      responses:
        '200':
          description:
            Returns ComponentsByAccount.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Component'
    patch:
      operationId: patchService
      responses:
        '200':
          description:
            Returns ComponentsByAccount.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Component'
components:
  schemas:
    Component:
      type: object
      properties:
        NAME:
          type: string
